:

*Vidi* ga kako leži u trave. (See him lying in the grass.)
*Videla* je kako je dete plakalo. (She saw the child crying.)
*Videlo* se da je njegovo raspoloženje pogoršalo. (It was seen that his mood had worsened.)
*Vidim* da me ne razumeš. (I see that you don't understand me.)
*Videti* ćeš da je ovo mesto veoma lepo. (You will see that this place is very nice.)